---
title: Red Wine Chicken and Mushroom Stew with Buttery Mash
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Red Wine Chicken and Mushroom Stew in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R12_W37_UK_QR15732-4_Main_low-5fc9af5f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/64ad73e7565e2133abaa44ab.pdf
course: main course
cuisine: British
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 508 kcal
  fat: 11.2 g
  saturated fat: 6 g
  carbohydrates: 63.9 g
